  "text": "(1.4) see the Remark 5.3 for further comments on this choice. This model consists of a 2 × 2 system of conservation laws with a C 0,1 but not C 1 flow. Note in fact that η/ρ = w ∈ [w,ŵ]. A 2 × 2 system of conservation laws with a flow having a similar C 0,1 regularity is presented in [CITATION_1] and studied in [1] .",
